    # 03

    
var findRepeatNumber = function(nums) {
    let temp = []
    for(let item of nums){
        if(temp.includes(item)){
                return item
        }else{
            temp.push(item)
        }
    }
};

let a = findRepeatNumber([2, 3, 1, 0, 2, 5, 3])
console.log('a',a)
